snippet.title: Forbidden Ingress Gameplay
snippet.description:
Our world is in danger! Grab your gun and stop these uninvited guests!

End of the twentieth century... Scientists were able to open a portal to another world. Something went wrong and now portals keep opening up all over the planet. Don't let anyone go through them!

💵--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1175200/Forbidden_Ingress/

🖱 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Always playing/testing the latest games from first impressions, game tips and occasionally walkthroughs. So if your new to the channel don't forget to 👊🏻 the like button and supporting this channel by subscribing.
